mdElement.text:
Cmpds are cascade=none from CmpdList.
Must MANUALLY manage deletion of AdHocCmd which only exist as long as the list that they are part of.
Copying AdHocCmpd to a new ListMember must create a NEW AdHocCmpd.
AdHocCmpd.originalAdHocCmpdId links ALL copies of the same AdHocCmpd. EACH copy has adHocCmpdId generated deNovo.
All joins are NOT navigable at the NscCmpd end and are NOT indexed EXCEPT NscCmpd->CmpdFragment which is bidirectional to enable the nc_cf_idx index as POP
